<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
        }

        .message-box {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #333;
        }

        p {
            color: #555;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .go-to-courses-btn {
            background-color: #4caf50;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-size: 16px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .go-to-courses-btn:hover {
            background-color: #45a049;
        }
    </style>
    <title>Tutor Application Confirmation</title>
</head>
<body>

<div class="message-box">
    <h1>Thank you for applying to be a tutor!</h1>
    <p>Your application has been successfully submitted. Please wait for administrative approval.</p>
    <p>You will receive a notification via email once your application is reviewed.</p>
    <p>Thank you for your patience and interest in tutoring.</p>
    
    <button class="go-to-courses-btn" onclick="window.location.href='/'">Go to Home</button>
</div>

</body>
</html>
